[Cannot input Japanese character]
1. Ctrl+Space to toggle Japanese(Mozc) mode
2. Left click the region displays character 'A' which is located on the upper-right corner of the entire window
3. Navigate to 'Input Mode(A)'
4. Select'Hiragana' changing it from 'Direct Input'

[Change keyboard layout in GUI]
1. Open 'Region & Language' setting
2. Add keyboard layouts
